des: Laura MacDonald's podcast will be discussing all things Real Estate Related. From tips for buying your first home, flying through the home selling process, catching up on the real estate market stats or even checking in to see what upcoming trends you can expect in home decor, this is the podcast to follow. Based out of Springfield, MO, you can also expect to hear great things about our community and it's development.
